host_about:
Hello, we are the VITA Team by Halldis, a group of professionals serving the vacation rental market for many years. 
We offer beautiful villas in Tuscany and apartments in several larger Italian cities such as Milan, Florence, Rome, Bologna, Venice, and Côte d'Azur. 
We have collaborated with Airbnb since 2013 and offer our homes to thousands of travelers. Be assured, we are more than happy to serve you as our next guest.

name: Vespucci 30
description: Welcome to our newly renovated apartment located in the central area of Florence, close to the train station and situated along the Arno River. We are excited to offer a renewed experience to our guests, so please note that old reviews do not reflect the current condition of the apartment.
host_about: I am a married mother of 2 from Wisconsin, USA.  Here in Florence Italy, alongside my husband Roberto, we have been running a small family housing business since 2017. Together with our team at LIVIT SRL, we are here to help make your stay as pleasant as possible.

name: ATЯА at Florence Cathedral
description:
ATЯА (At Rebecca’s Apartments) is a circuit of properties selected with the rigour and attention that our clients require.

ATЯА at Florence Cathedral enjoys a unique location , only 50 meters away from the Duomo and from a privileged view of the City, the Duomo and the Baptistery. It is located on the fourth floor of an historic building with elevator, terracotta floors, beamed ceilings and an original fresco.
host_about:
Rebecca's Apartments  lo dedichiamo a tutti coloro che vogliono per la loro vacanza il piacere dell'intimità della casa e la straordinarietà di un'esperienza autentica, senza dovere rinunciare ai servizi e al confort dell'hotel.
Ville, case e palazzi di lunga tradizione storica e famigliare nei luoghi più belli d'Italia diventano la casa della tua vacanza.  Il cerchio di Rebecca: straordinari luoghi comuni per vivere un'esperienza antica e sempre nuova.
